<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Life's Journey</h1>
  </header>
  <main>
    <div class="poem">
Life's journey is not always smooth
No flowers grow without rain, no humans glow without pain
We face our storms, we weather the test
And in the darkness, we find our best

The rain may pour, the pain may sting
But it's in these moments we learn to sing
A melody of strength, of resilience true
A symphony that echoes anew

No flowers grow without rain, no humans glow without pain
Yet from the depths, a beauty will reign
A light that shines, a heart that's bold
A soul that's tempered, like gold.
